c: 9
v: 108
t: "Ungaze ume (uthandaze) apho (kuloo masjid). Inene, iMasjid esiseko sayo sathi kwangomhla wokuqala saba phezu kobunyulu yiyona ifanelwe kukuba ume kuyo wena. Kuyo apho kukho amadoda athanda ukuzicoca azihlambulule imiphefumlo yawo. Ke kaloku uAllâh Uyabathanda abo bazicocayo bazihlambulule"